 on Seeking Alpha, to form an opinion on WPP (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WPPGF\" title=\"WPP plc\">OTCPK:WPPGF</a>) from an investor perspective. There's a secondary aim, though, for people interested in the media sector in general, to touch</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1802271297/image_1802271297.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743253-global-advertising-at-an-all-time-high-but-wpp-not-a-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 15:36:55"}, {"id": "4743252", "title": "DoorDash Through And Through: Maintaining With A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bullet-riddled rooms in Quneitra, Syria\" data-id=\"168260235\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1020px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/168260235/image_168260235.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\