{"id": "4743173", "title": "Meta's Orion Headsets Can Be Big, But Won't Be Impactful For Some Time", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086690371/image_2086690371.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Elegant female connecting metaverse looking faraway and smiling. Hallucination.\" data-id=\"2086690371\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"865px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086690371/image_2086690371.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086690371/image_2086690371.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086690371/image_2086690371.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086690371/image_2086690371.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086690371/image_2086690371.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086690371/image_2086690371.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086690371/image_2086690371.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086690371/image_2086690371.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">NanoStockk/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Meta Platforms (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/META\" title=\"Meta Platforms, Inc.\">META</a></span>) has two major catalysts at play that can generate scaled growth throughout the next two years. Meta is realizing strong user adoption of Meta AI for both content generation and search with</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086690371/image_2086690371.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743173-metas-orion-headsets-can-be-big-wont-be-impactful-for-time", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 15:07:00"}, {"id": "4743215", "title": "1 Big Dividend Stock To Sell And 1 Strong Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182443315/image_2182443315.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Wall with stick note written Overrated (Something praised but in fact isn\"t so impressive) and underrated (Something that is not talked about a lot, but offers great quality)' data-id=\"2182443315\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1110px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182443315/image_2182443315.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182443315/image_2182443315.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182443315/image_2182443315.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182443315/image_2182443315.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182443315/image_2182443315.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182443315/image_2182443315.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182443315/image_2182443315.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2182443315/image_2182443315.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\">